African Tea Prices Increase to $2.85 Per Kilogram, Broker Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-02-22T15:35:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-22/africa-tea-prices-increase-2-2-to-2-85-per-kilogram-at-sale-broker-says.html
African tea prices advanced to an
average of $2.85 per kilogram (2.2 pounds) at a weekly sale in  Mombasa ,  Kenya , from $2.79 a week earlier, Tea Brokers East
Africa Ltd. said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
